    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Dashboard Purpose",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# System Events Dashboard (Phase 2B)\n\nThis dashboard focuses on **system-level events** from core services:\n- Kernel messages (system events, network changes)\n- systemd/init (service lifecycle)\n- System daemons (rsyslog, cron, etc.)\n\n**Use case**: Troubleshooting system behavior, service restarts, and infrastructure changes\n\n**Visibility**: All log levels (info, warning, error) for comprehensive system view"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total System Events (6h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({log_source=\"rsyslog_syslog\", service_name=~\"kernel|systemd.*|$system_service\"}[6h]))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "System Services Found",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "count(count by (service_name) (count_over_time({log_source=\"rsyslog_syslog\", service_name=~\"kernel|systemd.*|$system_service\"}[6h])))"
